726
00:46:06,860 --> 00:46:08,520
So we have 9.

727
00:46:08,520 --> 00:46:11,580
And finally, the suit
that I need to select for,

728
00:46:11,580 --> 00:46:13,910
the extra card is diamonds.

729
00:46:13,910 --> 00:46:15,031
So this is an example.

730
00:46:15,031 --> 00:46:18,120


731
00:46:18,120 --> 00:46:21,940
And now we know, because
this is a bijection,

732
00:46:21,940 --> 00:46:25,030
