hands with four of a kind

733
00:46:25,030 --> 00:46:29,340
is equal to all these
types of sequences,

734
00:46:29,340 --> 00:46:33,780
all these types of
sequences that can--

735
00:46:33,780 --> 00:46:37,860
that are chosen according
to this representation.

736
00:46:37,860 --> 00:46:41,970
Well, we have 13 choices
for the first value.

737
00:46:41,970 --> 00:46:46,060
And given this first
value, we have 12 choices

738
00:46:46,060 --> 00:46:47,750
for the second value.

739
00:46:47,750 --> 00:46:53,840
And given those two, I have four
choices for the very last entry

740
00:46:53,840 --> 00:46:55,870
in this sequence.

741
00:46:55,870 --> 00:46:59,100
So this is the generalized
product rule that I'm using.

742
00:46:59,100 --> 00:47:05,950
So we see that the number of
sequences is equal to 13 times

743
00:47:05,950 --> 00:47:08,170
12 times 4.

744
00:47:08,170 --> 00:47:10,650
