746
00:47:15,250 --> 00:47:16,476
So how did we do this?

747
00:47:16,476 --> 00:47:18,017
This is the generalized
product rule.

748
00:47:18,017 --> 00:47:21,500


749
00:47:21,500 --> 00:47:24,560
If you divide this number
