1345
01:25:02,860 --> 01:25:04,940
So out of 3n elements.

1346
01:25:04,940 --> 01:25:07,810
And maybe I can
divide up the sets

1347
01:25:07,810 --> 01:25:09,780
in some kind of specific choice.

